A different way of doing something similar, with no code at all:<p>Copy the following into your browser URL bar:
&quot;data:text/html, <html contenteditable>&quot; 
(without quotation marks)

Sleepsort of course<p>#!/bin/bash<p>function f() {<p><pre><code>    sleep &quot;$1&quot;
    echo &quot;$1&quot;</code></pre>
}<p>while [ -n &quot;$1&quot; ]<p>do<p><pre><code>    f &quot;$1&quot; &
    shift
</code></pre>
done<p>wait
